                     <interp inst="t18211024-63-person633" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I took the prisoners in charge. Pratt had been stopped.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>BATTY'S Defence. I saw it laying in the road, and picked it up.</p>
